title: V.I.C.E. (Violent Incident Control Enforcement)
description:
The agents of V.I.C.E. (Violent Incident Control Enforcement) are super powered FBI agents, charged with bringing down domestic terrorists and the worst of all possible superhuman threats.

Published by Top Cow Productions, written by acclaimed TV writer Aron Coleite (Crossing Jordan) and illustrated by Tyler Kirkham (Darkness/Superman).


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
